{"prompt": "Generate a website for a personalized tutoring service. The website should be lively and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Bright Minds Tutoring</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #e53935; /* Red */\n            --secondary-color: #ffcdd2; /* Lighter red/pink */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --header-footer-bg: #f44336; /* Slightly darker red */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: var(--header-footer-bg);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #e53935 3px solid;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px #000000;\n        }\n\n        #showcase {\n            min-height: 400px;\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(229, 57, 53, 0.7), rgba(229, 57, 53, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x800/E53935/FFFFFF?text=Bright+Minds') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n\n        #showcase h2 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px #000000;\n        }\n\n        #showcase p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto 30px auto;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px #000000;\n        }\n\n        .button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background: #ffffff;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 12px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .button:hover {\n            background: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        #services, #about, #contact {\n            padding: 50px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #services h2, #about h2, #contact h2 {\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item, .about-item {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-color);\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover, .about-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3, .about-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n        }\n\n        .service-item p, .about-item p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n\n        #contact form {\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            display: inline-block;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        #contact label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        #contact input[type=\"text\"],\n        #contact input[type=\"email\"],\n        #contact textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        #contact textarea {\n            min-height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background: var(--header-footer-bg);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n\n        /* Animation */\n        @keyframes fadeInUp {\n            from {\n                opacity: 0;\n                transform: translateY(20px);\n            }\n            to {\n                opacity: 1;\n                transform: translateY(0);\n            }\n        }\n\n        .animated {\n            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out forwards;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Bright Minds Tutoring</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"showcase\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Unlock Your Child's Potential</h2>\n            <p>Personalized one-on-one tutoring designed to build confidence and foster a love for learning.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"button\">Get Started Today</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"service-item animated\">\n                <h3>Academic Support</h3>\n                <p>From elementary math to high school calculus, we provide tailored lessons to master any subject.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item animated\">\n                <h3>Test Preparation</h3>\n                <p>Boost scores for SAT, ACT, and other standardized tests with our expert guidance.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item animated\">\n                <h3>Homework Help</h3>\n                <p>Get timely assistance with assignments, ensuring understanding and completion.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>\n            <div class=\"about-item animated\">\n                <h3>Expert Tutors</h3>\n                <p>Our passionate educators are experienced professionals dedicated to student success.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"about-item animated\">\n                <h3>Personalized Approach</h3>\n                <p>We assess each student's unique needs and learning style to create a custom plan.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"about-item animated\">\n                <h3>Flexible Scheduling</h3>\n                <p>Sessions are conveniently scheduled to fit your busy lifestyle.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Contact Us</h2>\n            <p>Ready to see your child thrive? Get in touch to schedule a consultation!</p>\n            <form id=\"contact-form\">\n                <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n                <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n                <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" required></textarea>\n\n                <button type=\"submit\" class=\"button\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Bright Minds Tutoring. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {\n            const animatedElements = document.querySelectorAll('.animated');\n\n            const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {\n                entries.forEach(entry => {\n                    if (entry.isIntersecting) {\n                        entry.target.classList.add('animated');\n                        observer.unobserve(entry.target);\n                    }\n                });\n            }, {\n                threshold: 0.1\n            });\n\n            animatedElements.forEach(el => {\n                observer.observe(el);\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}